    Outpatient Clinics: (days & times will vary depending on outpatient clinic).<br />
    Day Medicine/Cancer Care Department: 9:30 a.m. – 12:30 p.m.<br />
    Long-Term Care Department: 4:00 p.m. – 6:00 p.m.<br />*@




